          <li>Physical books (paperback, hardcover)</li>
          <li>Digital books (ebook/PDF format)</li>
          <li>Prices displayed in USD</li>
          <li>Prices subject to change without notice</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Product Descriptions</h3>
