        <ul>
          <li>Printed on demand: 1-3 days production time</li>
          <li>Shipping: 5-10 business days (standard)</li>
          <li>International shipping times vary by location</li>
          <li>Risk of loss passes to you upon delivery to carrier</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Ebooks</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Instant delivery via email after payment confirmation</li>
          <li>Download link valid for 30 days (contact us if expired)</li>
          <li>No shipping charges</li>
        </ul>

        <p>See detailed <a href="/shipping">Shipping & Returns Policy</a> for complete information.</p>

        <h2>Refunds and Returns</h2>

        <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-red-200">
